Class GroupDto<T extends ReferableDto>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intland.codebeamer.persistence.dto.base.IdentifiableDto

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BaseDto, ReferenceHolderDto<ReferenceDto<T>>, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReadOnlyGroupDto
    Deprecated. 
    since CB-6.2 not used any more

    public class GroupDto<T extends ReferableDto>
extends NamedDto
implements ReferenceHolderDto<ReferenceDto<T>>
    The name GroupDto is misleading. A better name would be DomainDto, because it represents an access control domain for a codeBeamer entity, like a project, tracker, artifact, etc.
